import { React, useState } from 'react'; import { useFormik } from 'formik'; function Calc() { const [freightText, setFreight] = useState('0'); const [clearenceText, setClearence] = useState('0'); const [emailText, setEmail] = useState(' '); const formik = useFormik({ initialValues: { height: '', width: '', length: '', phone: '', email: '', address: '', value: '', clearence: '', }, onSubmit: values => { const phone = values.phone; const freight = (values.height + values.width + values.length) * 2; const clearence = values.value * values.clearence; const email = values.email; setFreight(freight) setClearence(clearence) setEmail(email) } }) return (

Grand Total

Freight: ${freightText}

Clearence: ${clearenceText}

One of our representatives will reach out to you at: {emailText}

); } export default Calc;
